Subject: perf docs: Update SPE doc to include default instructions group
Git-commit: edf93f2a24de5791bfaa15d82794e38e97c9498c
Patch-mainline: v6.18-rc1
References: perf-sle16.1-v6.19-userspace-update

The instructions group is now generated by default so update the doc to
reflect this. Also explain the period/downsampling mechanism in more
detail.

